  ⟨fun h => bounded_order_hom.ext <| hf.forall.2 <| fun_like.ext_iff.1 h, congr_arg _⟩
#align cancel_right cancel_right

  ⟨fun h =>
    bounded_order_hom.ext fun a => hg <| by rw [← bounded_order_hom.comp_apply, h, bounded_order_hom.comp_apply],
    congr_arg _⟩
#align cancel_left cancel_left
